00:02:02.260 --> 00:02:06.260
He says that we are happy because we give.

00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:10.259
Now, that's significant because that tells us that even when we force ourselves to give,

00:02:10.259 --> 00:02:12.259
even if we don't feel like it,

00:02:12.259 --> 00:02:15.259
we will experience happiness.

00:02:15.259 --> 00:02:19.259
At researchers today have confirmed with Jesus new all along,

00:02:19.259 --> 00:02:24.259
they even state possibly that giving releases endorphins in the brain

00:02:24.259 --> 00:02:27.259
that helps us with serenity and with contentment.

00:02:27.259 --> 00:02:31.259
So our first point is that giving makes us happy.

00:02:31.259 --> 00:02:38.599
For a second promise, look at Hebrews chapter 13 and verse 16.

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:41.599
Hebrews chapter 13 and verse 16.

00:02:41.599 --> 00:02:42.599
It says,

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:47.599
moreover, do not forget to do good and to share what you have with others.

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:51.599
