00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:38.600
so that we can be happy and fulfilled in life.

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:40.600
So that's our second promise.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:43.600
Giving puts us in a special relationship with Jehovah

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:46.600
and he will supply our needs.

